+    <h1>Diagnose the Broken Search</h1>
+    <p class="lede">Every researcher hits moments when the research is not working. What sets competent researchers apart is that they diagnose the problem accurately and apply a specific correction — instead of just searching harder. Each case below shows a search log. Read the symptom, name the diagnosis, pick the fix.</p>
+    <div class="howto"><b>How to use this:</b> two moves per case — diagnose, then correct. The searches use generic terms-and-connectors syntax; exact operators vary by platform (see <a href="../precision-search/index.html">Precision Search</a>). Finish with the closing-out protocol and make the closure call.</div>
+
