+    <h2>The closing-out protocol</h2>
+    <p class="secdesc">Narrowing finds the right things; closing out confirms you have not missed anything important. These are different jobs. Click each step, then make the closure calls below. If you cannot document why you stopped, you have not closed — you have just stopped.</p>
